Uh, it is real.

274
00:12:48,517 --> 00:12:50,437
Oh. Guess I’d better
do my part.

275
00:12:50,519 --> 00:12:54,059
(screams)

276
00:12:59,904 --> 00:13:02,784
Bring it on, chumps!

277
00:13:02,865 --> 00:13:04,775
