Fingers, fingers, fingers.

278
00:13:09,997 --> 00:13:10,997
LENNY:
What you doing, Moe?

279
00:13:11,081 --> 00:13:12,461
Drawing a wang
on Marmaduke?

280
00:13:12,541 --> 00:13:13,711
Heck, no.

281
00:13:13,793 --> 00:13:14,963
