is very clear.

351
00:17:11,155 --> 00:17:12,065
Never back down.

352
00:17:12,156 --> 00:17:13,696
Never admit a mistake.

353
00:17:13,782 --> 00:17:16,492
That’s why we’ve won
over half the wars we’ve fought.

354
00:17:17,870 --> 00:17:20,120
(sighs)

355
00:17:20,205 --> 00:17:23,995
Mom, we’ve got to stop them
from pacifying our town.

356
00:17:24,084 --> 00:17:25,254
Don’t worry.

357
00:17:25,335 --> 00:17:26,295
I have
a secret weapon--

358
00:17:26,378 --> 00:17:28,588
