than any gun.

359
00:17:28,672 --> 00:17:31,092
-Lisa’s face?
-A phone tree.

360
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:32,335
Huh?

361
00:17:32,426 --> 00:17:33,676
Well, you’d
better hurry.

362
00:17:33,761 --> 00:17:35,181
I don’t think Dad
can last much longer

363
00:17:35,262 --> 00:17:36,182
