364
00:17:36,263 --> 00:17:37,813
(coughing)

365
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:40,310
Dorothy’s daughter comes
every Sunday

366
00:17:40,392 --> 00:17:42,852
and brings all kinds
of wonderful soups.

367
00:17:42,936 --> 00:17:43,846
